      <guid>/talks/2024-04-joshua-pattern/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;the-joshua-pattern&#34;&gt;The Joshua Pattern&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Paul Bailey&lt;br&gt;
&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.neutron.studio/talks/&#34;&gt;neutron.studio/talks/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;but-first-a-little-about-me&#34;&gt;But First A Little About Me&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Born and raised in southern NJ&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Moved to Houston to work for a NASA contractor
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;met and married Shannon there (married ~21yrs)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Software developer for 20 years&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;For fun
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;computer programming&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;triathlon&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;jim-kautz-gaining-new-knowledge&#34;&gt;Jim Kautz: Gaining New Knowledge&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2 months ago&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;knowledge-is-half-of-the-equation&#34;&gt;Knowledge is half of the equation&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;we-also-must-be-doers&#34;&gt;We also must be Doers&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;scriptures&#34;&gt;Scriptures&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.biblegateway.com/passage/?search=Joshua+1%3A1-9&amp;version=NKJV&#34;&gt;Joshua 1:1-9&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
